data.description: Welcome HOME!  You've not seen a more put together home than this, located on the 11th green of Glenross Golf Club, with all the amenities that the community has to offer!  The .26 acre lot feels more like a never-ending expanse of green space for kids/pets/entertaining.  You might not want to go inside, instead choosing to enjoy the recently remodeled outdoor living space with gas fire pit and composite deck work that'll last a lifetime.  Head inside to find that there's nothing left to do but move in.  ALL NEW flooring throughout, NEWLY updated kitchen with several NEW appliances, NEW gas fireplace and shiplap surround....this feels like a new build!  Insulated, extra deep 3 car garage adds limitless storage, as does a completely finished basement with 5th bedroom option.  THIS is HOME!
